    </item>
    <item>
      <title>币安首席执行官谈特朗普和加密货币监管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-09/binance-ceo-on-trump-crypto-regulation-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Binance Holdings 首席执行官 Richard Teng 告诉 BTV 的 Lizzy Burden，加密货币的“未来是光明的”，并希望世界各国能够开始效仿美国在加密货币和人工智能方面的积极政策和监管，例如任命人工智能/加密货币沙皇并宣布加密货币战略储备计划。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-09/binance-ceo-on-trump-crypto-regulation-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 13:10:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新日铁澄清支出承诺以挽救与美国的协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/nippon-steel-clarifies-spending-pledge-in-effort-to-save-us-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新日本制铁公司公布了其在美国钢铁公司旗下美国钢厂的支出计划，这是其为争取工人和政界人士支持收购这家匹兹堡钢铁制造商而做出的最后一项努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/nippon-steel-clarifies-spending-pledge-in-effort-to-save-us-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 13:03:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
