      <title>西非作物前景恶化，可可价格创 7 个月新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/cocoa-hits-7-month-high-on-west-africa-crop-prospects-souring</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于西非生产前景黯淡，可可期货价格触及七个多月以来的最高水平，在库存处于历史低位的情况下对全球供应构成威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/cocoa-hits-7-month-high-on-west-africa-crop-prospects-souring</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 12:58:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列的斯莫特里奇称特朗普提供了推翻伊朗的机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/israel-s-smotrich-says-trump-offers-chance-to-overthrow-iran</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列财政部长兼内部安全内阁成员贝扎雷尔·斯莫特里奇表示，唐纳德·特朗普下个月的就职典礼为以色列提供了实现几个战略目标的机会：推翻伊朗政府、阻止巴勒斯坦国的建立、以及阻止在以色列边境重建黎巴嫩村庄。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/israel-s-smotrich-says-trump-offers-chance-to-overthrow-iran</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 12:53:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>温和多风天气缓解欧洲天然气价格下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/european-gas-prices-slip-as-mild-windy-weather-brings-respite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲天然气价格连续第五个交易日下跌，预计本月晚些时候温和多风的天气将有助于防止库存加速消耗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/european-gas-prices-slip-as-mild-windy-weather-brings-respite</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 07:49:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
